results.name: E.g.f. (1/5!)*sin^5(x)/cos(x) (coefficients of odd powers only).
link: Andrew Howroyd, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..100
formula: a(n) = (-1)^n/(3!*2^6) * Sum_{k = 0..n} ( 25^(n-k) - 3*9^(n-k) + 2 )*binomial(2*n+1, 2*k)*2^(2*k)*E(2*k, 1/2), where E(n,x) is the Euler polynomial of order n.
program: (PARI) a(n)={my(m=2*n+1, A=O(x*x^m)); m!*polcoef(sin(x + A)^5/cos(x + A), m)/120} \\ _Andrew Howroyd_, May 04 2020
